Tomcat Maven Plugin

 The Tomcat8 Maven Plugin provides goals to manipulate WAR projects within the {{{http://tomcat.apache.org/}Tomcat}} servlet container version 7.x

* Goals Overview

  The goals for this plugin are available here {{{./plugin-info.html}goals page}}.

* Usage

  Instructions on how to use the Tomcat Maven Plugin can be found on the {{{./usage.html}usage page}}.
